DescDetail: <<
"Mozilla left you.  Apple left you.  But we didn't."
TenFourFox is a port of Firefox 4 for PowerPC Macs.
A separate port is necessary because upstream no longer supports
10.4, nor PowerPC.
This packaging is also good for 10.5/ppc.  
<<
